             <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                                href=\"\/fr\/pret\/pret-reee\">\n                                                                Pr\u00eat REEE\n                                                            <\/a>\n                                                                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                        <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                                href=\"\/fr\/pret\/pret-investissement\">\n                                                                Pr\u00eat investissement\n                                                            <\/a>\n                                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                                href=\"\/fr\/pret\/carte-de-credit\">\n                                                                Carte de cr\u00e9dit\n                                                            <\/a>\n                                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                <\/div>\n                                                                                                \n                                                <div\n                                                    class=\"tab-pane fade \"\n                                                    id=\"vip-pane-3\"\n                                                    role=\"tabpanel\"\n                                                    aria-labelledby=\"vip-tab-3\"\n                                                    tabindex=\"0\">\n\n                                                    <div class=\"vip-mega-grid\">\n                                                        <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                                href=\"\/fr\/hypotheque\/programme-dachat-clef-en-main\">\n                                                                Programme d\u2019achat clef en main\n                                                            <\/a>\n                                                                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                        <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                                href=\"\/fr\/hypotheque\/pret-hypothecaire\">\n                                                                Pr\u00eat hypoth\u00e9caire\n                                                            <\/a>\n                                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                <\/div>\n                                                                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n\n                                    <\/div>\n                                <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                        \n                        <li class=\"nav-item d-xl-none\">\n                            <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/fr\/services\">Services<\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n                    \n                                            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                            <a class=\"nav-link\"\n                               href=\"\/fr\/construction\"\n                               >\n                                Notre \u00c9quipe\n                            <\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n                    \n                                            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                            <a class=\"nav-link\"\n                               href=\"\/fr\/carrieres\"\n                               >\n                                Carri\u00e8res\n                            <\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n                    \n                                            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                            <a class=\"nav-link\"\n                               href=\"\/fr\/partenaires\"\n                               >\n                                Partenaires\n                            <\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n                    \n                                            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                            <a class=\"nav-link\"\n                               href=\"\/fr\/contact\"\n                               >\n                                Contact\n                            <\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n                    \n                                            <li class=\"nav-item ms-xl-2 my-3 my-xl-0\">\n                            <a href=\"\/fr\/contact\"\n                               class=\"btn vip-btn-gold rounded-pill px-4 py-2 w-100 w-xl-auto\"\n                               >\n                                Obtenir un devis\n                            <\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/nav>\n\n    \n    \n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-4\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Qu\u2019est-ce qu\u2019un FERR ?<\/h2>\n                <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin-bottom: 20px;\"><\/div>\n\n                <div class=\"text-dark text-justify mb-4\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">\n                    <p>Le Fonds enregistr\u00e9 de revenu de retraite (FERR) est un type de compte de retraite qui permet de reporter l\u2019imp\u00f4t sur les fonds plac\u00e9s jusqu\u2019\u00e0 leur retrait. Il est souvent utilis\u00e9 pour convertir les fonds d&#039;un REER \u00e0 l&#039;\u00e2ge de la retraite.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div class=\"d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/rendez-vous\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm text-white fw-bold\">\n                        Faire une conversion\n                    <\/a>\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/contact\" class=\"btn btn-outline-dark rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm\">\n                        Contactez-nous\n                    <\/a>\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.equitable.ca\/fr\/nos-produits\/%C3%A9pargne-et-retraite\/calculateurs-%C3%A9pargne-et-retraite\/calculatrice-de-paiement-ferr\/\"\n                        target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-secondary rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm text-white\">\n                        Calculatrice FERR\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/A-cote-texte-FERR.jpg\" alt=\"FERR Retraite\" class=\"section-img rounded shadow hover-lift w-100 object-fit-cover\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 bg-white border-start border-4 border-warning\">\n                    <div class=\"d-flex\">\n                        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 me-3 text-warning\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-info-circle fa-2x\"><\/i>\n                        <\/div>\n                        <div>\n                            <ul class=\"list-unstyled mb-0 text-dark\">\n                                <li class=\"mb-2\">- Les conditions de conversion du REER en FERR varient selon les r\u00e8gles de l&#039;ARC.<\/li>\n                                <li>- Une fois dans un FERR, des retraits minimums annuels sont obligatoires pour maintenir l&#039;int\u00e9grit\u00e9 fiscale.<\/li>\n                            <\/ul>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h2 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color:var(--primary-color);\">Les points cl\u00e9s \u00e0 savoir sur le FERR<\/h2>\n            <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin: 15px auto;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"row g-4 justify-content-center\">\n            \n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/lending_2856892.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Conversion du REER<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Le REER doit \u00eatre transform\u00e9 en FERR au plus tard \u00e0 71 ans.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/alert_14356955.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Retraits et Revenus<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Les retraits d&#039;un FERR sont imposables comme revenu.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/delete_11502976.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Limites de Retrait<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Des limites minimales s&#039;appliquent annuellement.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/growth_2910299.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Investissements<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Le FERR peut contenir divers actifs (actions, obligations, etc.).<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/business_13389610.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Transf\u00e9rabilit\u00e9<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Transf\u00e9rable entre institutions sans incidence fiscale.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/friendship_7959236.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Conjoint Survivant<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Le conjoint peut continuer \u00e0 recevoir les paiements en cas de d\u00e9c\u00e8s.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/ferr\/limited-time_9449615.png\" width=\"64\" alt=\"Icone\"><\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Dur\u00e9e de vie limit\u00e9e<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small\">Certains FERR n\u00e9cessitent une liquidation apr\u00e8s un certain \u00e2ge.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"mt-5 text-center px-lg-5\">\n            <p class=\"text-muted fst-italic fs-5\">\"Il est recommand\u00e9 de consulter un conseiller pour comprendre les r\u00e8g